IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
  PROGRAM-ID. "scanf_demo".
DATA DIVISION.
  01 READ PICTURE IS S9999.
  01 A PICTURE IS 9.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN.
  DISPLAY "Please enter a number of up to four digits".
  CALL scanf USING "%4d" AS PRIMITIVE BY REFERENCE READ AS PRIMITIVE.
  DISPLAY "You entered " READ.

  IF READ > 7 THEN
    DISPLAY READ " is larger than 7"
  ELSE
    DISPLAY READ " is equal to or lower than 7!"
  END.

  DISPLAY "DONE".

  END.